=== 多人模式 ===
《黑色行動冷戰》“將冷戰武器和裝備帶入了下一代的多人遊戲”<ref>{{Citation|title=Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War Officially Revealed, Out in November - IGN|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/call-of-duty-black-ops-cold-war-november-13-release-date-ps5-xbox-series-x|accessdate=2020-09-01|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418001100/https://www.ign.com/articles/call-of-duty-black-ops-cold-war-november-13-release-date-ps5-xbox-series-x|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並支援跨平台配對功能，所有玩家不分平台都能夠一起連線對戰。同由動視發行的免費[[大逃杀游戏|大逃殺遊戲]]《[[使命召唤：战争地带|決勝時刻：現代戰域]]》將在《黑色行動冷戰》中繼續登場並共享部分遊戲內容和進度系統，玩家所收集到的物品也可同時在這兩款遊戲中使用。<ref>{{Cite web|title=隆重宣布《決勝時刻®：黑色行動冷戰》|url=https://news.blizzard.com/zh-tw/blizzard/23507727/%E9%9A%86%E9%87%8D%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E3%80%8A%E6%B1%BA%E5%8B%9D%E6%99%82%E5%88%BB%C2%AE%EF%BC%9A%E9%BB%91%E8%89%B2%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E5%86%B7%E6%88%B0%E3%80%8B|accessdate=2020-08-31|author=|date=|format=|work=news.blizzard.com|publisher=|language=zh-tw|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120203946/https://news.blizzard.com/zh-tw/blizzard/23507727/%E9%9A%86%E9%87%8D%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E3%80%8A%E6%B1%BA%E5%8B%9D%E6%99%82%E5%88%BB%C2%AE%EF%BC%9A%E9%BB%91%E8%89%B2%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E5%86%B7%E6%88%B0%E3%80%8B|dead-url=no}}</ref>
