=== 殭屍模式 ===
玩家可以单人也可以联机进行游玩。玩家将探索冷戰實驗，這些實驗釋放出新的殭屍威脅，而最终目的就是关停整个设施并顺利离开此地。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The iconic Black Ops series is back with Call of Duty®: Black Ops Cold War|url=https://us.shop.battle.net/en-us/product/call-of-duty-black-ops-cold-war?p=73998|accessdate=2020-09-01|author=|date=|format=|work=us.shop.battle.net|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411081916/https://us.shop.battle.net/en-us/product/call-of-duty-black-ops-cold-war?p=73998|dead-url=no}}</ref>

